aption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510100" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams.jpg" alt="" width="2158" height="1424" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams.jpg 2158w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-400x264.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-800x528.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-696x459.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-1392x919.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-1068x705.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2158px) 100vw, 2158px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510100" class="wp-caption-text">利维·布朗在《这个小镇》中饰演但丁·威廉姆斯。信用：英国广播公司</figcaption></figure><p>另一张照片显示布朗在唱片店里扮演但丁·威廉姆斯，在第三张照片中，他与奥斯汀的珍妮·基夫在更衣室里分享了片刻。 </p><figure id="attachment_3510104" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510104" style="width: 2132px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3510104 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe-and-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams.jpg" alt="" width="2132" height="1420" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe-and-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams.jpg 2132w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe-and-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-400x266.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe-and-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe-and-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-696x464.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe-and-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-1392x927.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe-and-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-1068x711.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2132px) 100vw, 2132px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510104" class="wp-caption-text">在《这个小镇》中，伊芙·奥斯汀饰演珍妮·基夫，利维·布朗饰演但丁·威廉姆斯。信用：英国广播公司</figcaption></figure><p>道克瑞的艾丝黛拉和平诺克的德斯·威廉姆斯也被拍到准备表演。与此同时，另一张照片显示罗斯、帕克斯、布朗和奥斯汀一起在仓库里。 </p><figure id="attachment_3510106" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510106" style="width: 2172px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510106" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Michelle-Dockery-as-Estella-and-Nicholas-Pinnock-as-Deuce-Williams.jpg" alt="" width="2172" height="1434" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Michelle-Dockery-as-Estella-and-Nicholas-Pinnock-as-Deuce-Williams.jpg 2172w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Michelle-Dockery-as-Estella-and-Nicholas-Pinnock-as-Deuce-Williams-400x264.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Michelle-Dockery-as-Estella-and-Nicholas-Pinnock-as-Deuce-Williams-800x528.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Michelle-Dockery-as-Estella-and-Nicholas-Pinnock-as-Deuce-Williams-696x460.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Michelle-Dockery-as-Estella-and-Nicholas-Pinnock-as-Deuce-Williams-1392x919.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Michelle-Dockery-as-Estella-and-Nicholas-Pinnock-as-Deuce-Williams-1068x705.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2172px) 100vw, 2172px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510106" class="wp-caption-text">在《这个小镇》中，米歇尔·道克瑞 (Michelle Dockery) 饰演艾丝黛拉 (Estella)，尼古拉斯·平诺克 (Nicholas Pinnock) 饰演 Deuce Williams。信用：英国广播公司</figcaption></figure><p><em>《这个小镇》</em>将与隶属于环球音乐集团的 Mercury Studios 联合制作，后者将引进知名音乐家来“帮助为 Knight 令人难以置信的故事奠定背景”（据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-67009292">BBC</a>报道）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3510107" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510107" style="width: 2172px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510107" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ben-Rose-as-Bardon-Quinn-Freya-Parks-as-Fiona-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-and-Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe.-BBC.jpg" alt="" width="2172" height="1450" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ben-Rose-as-Bardon-Quinn-Freya-Parks-as-Fiona-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-and-Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe.-BBC.jpg 2172w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ben-Rose-as-Bardon-Quinn-Freya-Parks-as-Fiona-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-and-Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe.-BBC-400x267.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ben-Rose-as-Bardon-Quinn-Freya-Parks-as-Fiona-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-and-Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe.-BBC-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ben-Rose-as-Bardon-Quinn-Freya-Parks-as-Fiona-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-and-Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe.-BBC-696x465.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ben-Rose-as-Bardon-Quinn-Freya-Parks-as-Fiona-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-and-Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe.-BBC-1392x929.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ben-Rose-as-Bardon-Quinn-Freya-Parks-as-Fiona-Levi-Brown-as-Dante-Williams-and-Eve-Austin-as-Jeannie-Keefe.-BBC-1068x713.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2172px) 100vw, 2172px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510107" class="wp-caption-text">在《这个小镇》中，本·罗斯 (Ben Rose) 饰演巴登·奎恩 (Bardon Quinn)，芙蕾雅·帕克斯 (Freya Parks) 饰演菲奥娜 (Fiona)，利维·布朗 (Levi Brown) 饰演但丁·威廉姆斯 (Dante Williams)，伊芙·奥斯汀 (Eve Austin) 饰演珍妮·基夫 (Jeannie Keefe)。信用：英国广播公司</figcaption></figure><p>获得水星奖提名的音乐家、小说家兼诗人 Kae Tempest 和制作人 Dan Carey 创作了乐队在银幕上表演的歌曲。</p><p>谈起该剧，奈特说道：“这是一个我经历过、非常了解的时代，其中涉及到我觉得和我一起长大的角色。我希望来自世界各地的人们能够对此产生共鸣。”</p><p> <em>《这座小镇》</em>将于 2024 年在 BBC One 和 BBC iPlayer 上播出。</p><p>奈特与<em>《浴血黑帮》</em>一样，因编剧和导演了 2013 年汤姆·哈迪主演的《<em>洛克</em>》和杰森·斯坦森主演的<em>《蜂鸟》</em>而闻名。他的其他作品包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bbc">BBC</a>剧集<em>Taboo</em> 、 <em>Spencer</em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>剧集<em>See</em> 。</p><p>早在三月份，就有报道称，在原编剧达蒙·林德洛夫（ <em>《迷失</em>》）和贾斯汀·布里特-吉布森离开该项目后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/peaky-blinders-creator-steven-knight-to-write-star-wars-movie-3419045">，奈特正在为一部新的<em>《星球大战》</em>电影编写剧本</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/rthis-town-first-look-at-peaky-blinders-creators-steven-knight-new-drama-3510090">《This Town》帖子：《Peaky Blinders》创作者 Steven Knight 的新剧抢先看，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
